============================================================
ALPHA-PRIME v2.0 - Docker Ignore Rules
============================================================
Excludes files from Docker build context to:
- Reduce image size (target: <500MB)
- Speed up builds (exclude 10,000+ cache files)
- Prevent secrets leakage
- Avoid unnecessary cache invalidation
Build context sent to Docker daemon = project root MINUS these patterns
============================================================


============================================================
CRITICAL - SECRETS & CREDENTIALS
============================================================
Never bake real credentials or private keys into Docker images.

# Core env files with real secrets
.env
**/.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# Cloud and SSH credentials
**/.aws
**/.ssh

# Key material and certificates
*.key
*.pem
*.p12

# Explicit secret config files
secrets.yaml
credentials.json

# Any filename containing secret-like keywords (defensive)
**/*secret*
**/*Secret*
**/*SECRET*
**/*password*
**/*Password*
**/*PASSWORD*
**/*token*
**/*Token*
**/*TOKEN*

# Auth artifacts (tokens, browser exports, local auth helpers)
auth/
auth/**


============================================================
RUNTIME DATA (USER-SPECIFIC, REGENERATED IN CONTAINER)
============================================================
Exclude user-specific trading state, logs, caches, and backups.

# Core trading state and analytics artifacts
data/portfolio.json
data/trade_history.csv
data/strategy_performance.json
data/drift_metrics.json
data/execution_analytics.csv

# Cache: SEC filings, news, social, market data
data/cache/
data/cache/**

# Backups (portfolio snapshots, state archives)
backups/
backups/**

# Logs: runtime logs and rotations
logs/
logs/**

# Generic temporary/backup files
*.tmp
*.bak

# Keep directory skeletons for mounts / runtime usage
!data/.gitkeep
!logs/.gitkeep


